item.title: CVE-2023-49695|2024-10-08T19:27:02.245Z -- elecom%20co.%2Cltd. -- wrc-x3000gsn
item.description: OS command injection vulnerability in WRC-X3000GSN v1.0.2, WRC-X3000GS v1.0.24 and earlier, and WRC-X3000GSA v1.0.24 and earlier allows a network-adjacent attacker with an administrative privilege to execute an arbitrary OS command by sending a specially crafted request to the product.
